oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Photograph of the grave of Pvt. Frank M. Ring, Co. A, 114th MG Battn., 30th Div.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This photograph shows the grave of Pvt. Frank M. Ring, Co. A, 114th MG Battn., 30th Div. in the Somme Cemetery. Frank Ring, from Franklin, Tennessee, was killed-in-action October 9, 1918. The photograph was taken in 1998 from nearly the exact same spot as seen in [GWfran132] in 1932. It was taken by Frank Ring's descendants.
